body: I see what the below commenter means, a few pages do indeed have wonky anatomy and proportions. Aside from those relatively minor details though it's a nicely drawn book that's a great change of pace from the usual orc/ugly bastard raping the elf.

This was looking good up until page 12. The broken shoulders and neck on the elf just murdered my boner. It returned on page 14 into 15, only to be killed again on page 19.

Damn it.
